#. type: multicols*
#: sections/scenarios.tex:10
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Heroes III is a Scenario-driven game.\n"
"In the first step of each game's setup, you choose a \\textbf{Scenario} from the Mission Book.\n"
"Scenarios have a backstory and determine the map layout, the starting conditions for players, and the requirements for winning the Scenario.\n"
"Furthermore, Scenarios can introduce entirely unique game rules.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"英雄无敌3是一款剧本驱动的游戏。%\n"
"在每局游戏准备流程的第一步，你从任务书中选择一个\\textbf{剧本}。%\n"
"剧本拥有背景故事，并决定地图布局、玩家的起始条件，以及赢得该剧本的要求。%\n"
"此外，剧本还可以引入完全独特的游戏规则。\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/scenarios.tex:14
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\bigskip\n"
"\\bigskip\n"
"\\subheader{Scenario Types}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\begin{center} \\transparent{0.2}\\includegraphics[width=0.6\\linewidth]{\\art/tome_of_earth_magic.png}\n"
"\\end{center}\n"
"\\subheader{剧本类型}\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/scenarios.tex:18
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\subsection*{Clash}\n"
"A fully competitive mode.\n"
"Your opponents control Neutral Units in your Combat.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\subsection*{冲突}\n"
"完全竞争模式。%\n"
"你的对手在你的战斗中控制中立单位。\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/scenarios.tex:23
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\subsection*{Campaign}\n"
"A single-player mode\\index{Solo Mode} of interconnected Scenarios against an enemy AI.\n"
"For rules unique to Solo Mode, see \\pagelink{Campaign}{the Campaign rules}.\n"
"Further rule changes are detailed in the Campaign Mission Books.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\subsection*{战役}\n"
"一种单人模式\\index{单人模式}，由相互关联的剧本组成，对抗敌方AI。%\n"
"关于单人模式的专属规则，见\\pagelink{Campaign}{战役规则}。%\n"
"进一步的规则变更详见战役任务书。\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/scenarios.tex:26
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\subsection*{Alliance}\n"
"Usually a 2 vs.~2 team-based mode with expanded opportunities to \\pagelink{Trading}{trade} between allied players.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\subsection*{同盟}\n"
"通常为2对2的团队模式，同盟玩家之间有更多\\pagelink{Trading}{交易}机会。\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/scenarios.tex:30
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\subsection*{Cooperative}\n"
"A Cooperative mode where everyone shares the same goal.\n"
"\\pagelink{AI Units}{The AI rules} and expanded \\pagelink{Trading}{Trading rules} apply here.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\subsection*{合作}\n"
"一种合作模式，所有人共享同一个目标。%\n"
"\\pagelink{AI Units}{AI规则}和扩展的\\pagelink{Trading}{交易规则}在此适用。\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/scenarios.tex:34
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\subsection*{Tournament}\n"
"A 1 vs.~1 mode with a different way of building the Map and scoring.\n"
"See \\pagelink{Tournament Mode}{Tournament Mode}.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\subsection*{锦标赛}\n"
"一种1对1模式，采用不同的地图构建和计分方式。%\n"
"参见\\pagelink{Tournament Mode}{锦标赛模式}。\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/scenarios.tex:38
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\bigskip\n"
"\\begin{expansion}[before=\\vspace*{-10mm}]{battlefield}\n"
"  \\pagelink{Adventure and Skirmish Modes}{Battlefield Expansion} introduces two focused 1 vs.~1 game modes \\textbf{which work without Scenarios}.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\begin{expansion}[beforeafter skip balanced=0pt]{battlefield}\n"
"  \\pagelink{Adventure and Skirmish Modes}{战场扩展}引入了两种专门的1对1的游戏模式，\\textbf{无需剧本即可进行}。\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/scenarios.tex:41
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  \\subsection*{Adventure}\n"
"  The Map exploration is replaced with Adventure cards, culminating in a tactical combat on a large hexagonal battlefield, see \\pagelink{Adventure}{Adventure Mode} for details.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"  \\subsection*{冒险}\n"
"  地图探索由冒险牌取代，最终在大型六边格战场上进行一场战术战斗，详情见\\pagelink{Adventure}{冒险模式}。\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/scenarios.tex:45
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  \\subsection*{Skirmish}\n"
"  Skip the exploration phase and engage directly in tactical combat, see \\pagelink{Skirmish}{Skirmish Mode} for details.\n"
"\\end{expansion}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"  \\subsection*{遭遇战}\n"
"  跳过探索阶段并直接进入战术战斗，详见\\pagelink{Skirmish}{遭遇战模式}。\n"
"\\end{expansion}\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/scenarios.tex:48
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\vspace*{1em}\n"
"\\subheader{Scenario Difficulty}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\vspace*{1em}\n"
"\\subheader{剧本难度}\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/scenarios.tex:57
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"You can modify the \\pagetarget{Difficulty}{Difficulty} of a Scenario.\n"
"There are four different Difficulties, each with a different starting bonus\\index{Starting Bonus} that you receive during \\pagelink{setupdifficulty}{step \\ref*{setupdifficulty} of the setup}:\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\item \\textbf{Easy} – Roll 2 Resource Dice \\svg{resource_die} and receive Resources from both – OR – \\textbf{Search} (2) the Artifact Deck, twice.\n"
"  \\item \\textbf{Normal} – Roll 2 Resource Dice \\svg{resource_die} and receive the Resources from one of them – OR – \\textbf{Search} (2) the Artifact Deck.\n"
"  \\item \\textbf{Hard} – Roll 1 Resource Die \\svg{resource_die} and receive the Resources on it – OR – reveal cards from the top of the Artifact Deck until you find 1 Minor Artifact and add it to your hand.\n"
"  \\item \\textbf{Impossible} – No starting bonus.\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"你可以修改一个剧本的\\pagetarget{Difficulty}{难度}。%\n"
"共有四种不同难度，每种都有不同的起始奖励\\index{起始奖励}，你会在\\pagelink{setupdifficulty}{准备的第\\ref*{setupdifficulty}步}中获得这些奖励：\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\item \\textbf{简单}——掷2个资源骰\\svg{resource_die}，并获得两者的资源——或者——对神器牌堆进行两次\\textbf{搜寻（2）}。\n"
"  \\item \\textbf{普通}——掷2个资源骰\\svg{resource_die}，并获得其中一个的资源——或者——对神器牌堆进行\\textbf{搜寻（2）}。\n"
"  \\item \\textbf{困难}——掷1个资源骰\\svg{resource_die}，并获得其上的资源——或者——从神器牌堆顶展示牌，直到你找到1件次级神器，并将其加入你的手牌。\n"
"  \\item \\textbf{极难}——无起始奖励。\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/scenarios.tex:59
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Campaign Scenarios have unique bonuses that \\textbf{replace} the regular starting bonus.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"战役剧本具有独特奖励，会\\textbf{取代}常规起始奖励。\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/scenarios.tex:64
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\pagelink{Playerdecks}{Searching \\textbf{Artifacts}} is explained in the general card rules.\n"
"Artifacts received from a starting bonus must be placed into your \\textbf{hand} and not shuffled into your Starting Deck.\n"
"If you searched for any Artifacts, shuffle the Artifact Deck and its Discard Pile\\index{Discard Pile} together afterwards, and then discard one Artifact from the top to form the Artifact Discard Pile again.\\par\n"
"The chosen Difficulty also determines the number and type of Neutral Units that are encountered during Neutral Combat according to the \\hyperlink{Difficulty Table}{table} on the back cover of the book.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\pagelink{Playerdecks}{搜寻\\textbf{神器}}在通用卡牌规则中解释。%\n"
"从起始奖励获得的神器必须放入你的\\textbf{手牌}，而不是洗入你的起始牌堆。%\n"
"如果你搜寻过任何神器，之后将神器牌堆和其弃牌堆\\index{弃牌堆}一起洗混，然后从牌堆顶弃置一张神器，以重新形成神器弃牌堆。\\par\n"
"所选择的难度还会根据封底\\hyperlink{Difficulty Table}{表格}决定在中立战斗中遭遇的中立单位的数量和类型。\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/scenarios.tex:68
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\vfill\n"
"\\includegraphics[width=\\linewidth]{\\art/archer.jpg}\n"
"\\columnbreak\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\vfill\n"
"\\includegraphics[width=\\linewidth]{\\art/archer.jpg}\n"
"\\columnbreak\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/scenarios.tex:73
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\pagetarget{End}{\\subheader{Victory conditions}}\n"
"All Scenarios have their victory conditions\\index{Victory Conditions} described in the Mission Book.\n"
"The most common victory conditions require defeating certain enemy Towns, Heroes, or Neutral Units; capturing the Grail; or controlling certain or most Locations over time.\n"
"Whenever a player achieves a victory condition, the game ends at the end of the Round, unless stated otherwise.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\pagetarget{End}{\\subheader{胜利条件}}\n"
"所有剧本的胜利条件\\index{胜利条件}均在任务书中说明。%\n"
"最常见的胜利条件要求击败特定的敌方城镇、英雄或中立单位；夺取圣杯；或在一段时间内控制特定或大多数地点。%\n"
"每当一名玩家达成胜利条件时，除非另有说明，游戏会在该轮结束时结束。\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/scenarios.tex:85
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"In addition, it is always possible to be \\textbf{eliminated} from any Scenario in the following ways:\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\item Play 3 full Rounds without controlling a Town or a Settlement.\n"
"    Count the number of Rounds left using any suitable component.\n"
"  \\item Lose Combat with your \\textbf{Main Hero} when you have no Towns or Settlements left, including when defending your last Town or Settlement.\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"Eliminated players are immediately removed from the game.\n"
"Discard their Faction Cubes and Hero models from the Map.\n"
"Treat the cards in their Deck as being removed from the game for the rest of the Scenario.\n"
"If you are eliminated, you may still participate in the game by controlling Neutral Units.\\par\n"
"\\note{4}{If you eliminate all enemy Factions, you immediately win the Scenario.}\\par\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"此外，在任何剧本中，玩家都可能通过以下方式\\textbf{被淘汰}出局：\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\item 连续进行3个完整轮次，且未控制任何城镇或定居点。%\n"
"    使用任何合适的组件记录剩余轮次数。\n"
"  \\item 当你没有剩余城镇或定居点时，你的\\textbf{主英雄}在战斗中失败，包括防守你最后一个城镇或定居点。\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"被淘汰的玩家立即从游戏中移除。%\n"
"将其阵营方块和英雄模型从地图上弃置。%\n"
"在本剧本剩余时间内，将其牌堆中的牌视为已从游戏中移除。%\n"
"如果你被淘汰，你仍可通过控制中立单位参与游戏。\\par\n"
"\\note{4}{如果你淘汰所有敌方阵营，你立即赢得该剧本。}\\par\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/scenarios.tex:89
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
#| msgid ""
#| "In \\textbf{Clash} Scenarios with three or more players, when you collect \\textbf{a Faction Cube} from every enemy player, you win the Scenario.\n"
#| "You gain such Faction Cubes by defeating Main Heroes or conquering enemy Towns.\n"
#| "Other Scenario-specific rules may also modify the outcome of collecting Faction Cubes.\n"
#| "\n"
msgid ""
"In \\textbf{Clash} Scenarios with three or more players, when you collect \\textbf{a Faction Cube} from every enemy player, you win the Scenario.\n"
"You gain such Faction Cubes by defeating enemy Heroes or conquering enemy Towns.\n"
"Other Scenario-specific rules may also modify the outcome of collecting Faction Cubes.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"在\\textbf{冲突}剧本中有三名或更多玩家时，当你从每位敌方玩家处收集到\\textbf{一个阵营方块}，你赢得该剧本。%\n"
"你通过击败主英雄或征服敌方城镇来获得这些阵营方块。%\n"
"剧本特定规则也可能改变收集阵营方块的结果。\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/scenarios.tex:91
#, no-wrap
msgid "After finishing a \\textbf{Solo Campaign} Scenario, see the \\pagelink{Campaign}{Campaign section} for how to prepare for the next Scenario of the Campaign."
msgstr "完成\\textbf{单人战役}剧本后，参见\\pagelink{Campaign}{战役章节}，了解如何为该战役的下一个剧本做准备。"
